# Settlement engine freeze

Billing & Settlement Engine is **feature complete**. See `docs/SETTLEMENT_ENGINE_FREEZE.md`.

## Do not modify settlement mathematics unless

- An invariant or production validation script fails, OR
- A documented **BR-*** business rule change was approved

Never fix a single resident in code or SQL.

## Default work mode

- **UX only:** copy, layout, collapsibles, hero metrics, admin/resident tiers
- Load money via `loadVacatingBillingPresentation` / `loadVacatingBillingPresentationBundle` only
- Do not add alternate refund or notice formulas in components

## If engine change is required

1. Reproduce failure signature  
2. One fix in mapped SSOT module (`docs/BILLING_ENGINE_INVARIANTS.md`)  
3. Regression test + re-run `npm run test:billing-settlement` and prod validator
